Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:54.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中的願望  搖曳的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:05.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓飛雪滑過臉頰…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:12.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揮之不去的後悔  緊系過去的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風的細語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:18.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一觸即散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:26.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒空中夾雜著寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:34.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越過了眼中的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:42.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在想給你的旋律  遙指著初星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:50.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天空拼湊出的未來  手指間露出的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:58.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊  想要實現在此看見的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:04.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:51.89,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}長い間積もっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:58.72,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}すれ違いに気付いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:09.40,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}だからその想いを救える場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:16.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}置きに行こう　今ならできるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:25.30,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}淡い記憶辿りながら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:30.40,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}糸と糸たぐり寄せていつか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:33.40,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}僕らは出会う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:43.30,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}幼い願い満ち溢れ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:59.66,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}奇跡を起こすの　この町に　ah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:10.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}無邪気に君と笑うあの日と変わらない時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:21.16,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ふと手を伸ばせばそこに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:48.66,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}白く光る星のカケラ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:53.82,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}それは心の奥刻まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:56.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}淡いぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:23:06.73,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}幼い過ちさえほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:24.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}触れたら溶けてく雪のように
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:51.89,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}長時間的積累
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:58.72,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}察覺到擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:09.40,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}所以將思念帶往救贖之地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:16.58,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}安放在那裡  現在一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:25.30,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}隨著談談記憶的到達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:30.40,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}線與線終將會交織在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:33.40,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我們相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:43.30,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}小小的願望得以滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:59.66,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在這個小鎮  降臨奇跡  ah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:10.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}與你天真的笑容一樣不變的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:21.16,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}忽而把手伸向那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:48.66,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}星星的碎片閃耀著白光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:53.82,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}那是刻在心靈深處的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:56.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}點點溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:23:06.73,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就連兒時的那些過錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:24.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}也彷彿雪花一樣漸漸消融
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸先生  你的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春  不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸先生  怪獸先生他生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生病？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別介意  反正已經很舊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近正想著要換一個新的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思  還要特意過來接我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.56,0:00:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.51,0:01:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  諾艾爾也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  諾艾爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  一起來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也邀請過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.71,0:01:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是被拒絕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾要和怪獸先生在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.38,0:01:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸…先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸先生
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:15.92,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(395,270)}「我所失去的東西」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫了我們這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點小事不要在意  上班順路而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝什麼帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我們去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點兒  快點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不坐一會兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下多可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次來這邊  不好好玩一下怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初三學生都沒有時間可以好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北美祭的演出節目也還沒有決定下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香沒有準備什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小時候一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這麼說來  小春也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小時候比起來沒什麼變化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候開始  就照顧著柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家裡面也是最成熟的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這樣呢  我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  看上去成熟是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我戴上的話也會一樣變得成熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去看風景了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好東西要留到最後再去看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是諾艾爾和汐音也能一起來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戶川同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  沒有跟妳說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我邀請了汐音  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那天我有安排了  很多年前就約好了的」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是委婉地拒絕了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟不是直率的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不疼  不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死啦  疼死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子疼得快要死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:05:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸先生  不要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了  千萬不能死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要激動  不要激動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦  剛才是我在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為諾艾爾  怪獸先生他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  才不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑而已  開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是小小開了一個玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好知道啦  我也會幫怪獸先生治病的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已經走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是什麼都沒有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在這種地方等上一個小時？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道  可是不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是說過要好好享受這裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個跟這個說的才不是一個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有個地方能坐坐就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還帶著這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著這是吃便當的必備用品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是剛好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  看我的看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是店裡最有人氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來不是自己做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做倒是媽媽做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它們弄得這麼好看的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦  知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前好像也有過像這樣大家一起分著吃便當的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天文臺？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是只有小春忘記帶便當了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是乃乃香拜託大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來大家把便當放在一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來乃乃香也是幹勁十足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果最後變成我吃到了最豪華的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  乃乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了  有心事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戀愛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  我們吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸先生會好起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這麼擔心它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也會感到欣慰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有諾艾爾幫得上忙的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼幫我按著它的手臂  讓它別亂動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不點？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不跟著小春她們一起出門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們叫上妳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太遠了  看不到飛碟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話不就只能待在這附近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  幫我好好按住它吧  諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「走吧」算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一句話就把我給打發了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連乃乃香也這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這裡也太大了  要走多久才到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估計差不多快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向沒有錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸給了我地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\move(440,100,427,107)\bord0\1c505050\fs16\t(\fs15)\frz-3}這裡！\N第四行\N從右數第6個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找這個目標建築
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給爸爸打個電話  確認一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個的話  剛剛已經看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香妳什麼都不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有錯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了確認一下  我們再走一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話怪獸先生就會好起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有疼痛的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然太馬虎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  再進行一次手術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定沒錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想是這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果因為柚季  我們才迷路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在先別理我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去打水  妳休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有心事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說我們是硬跟著過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是回避一下的比較好？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我一直很害怕見到媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想現在也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒有和大家說想見媽媽一面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就不會來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我只看過照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳媽媽看起來很溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她非常溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常溫柔  總是笑容滿面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是抱著我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖洋洋的  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握著的手卻總是冷冰冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7年前  從小鎮離開後不久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才知道搬家是為了媽媽的治療
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  媽媽還是走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我十分悲傷  感到很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得所有事物都變得漆黑一片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時候  我就不想再回憶起往事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的聲音和笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和媽媽一起生活過的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就沒有發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無數次  無數次的和自己說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  真的變得不再痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心不再疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  和大家的珍貴記憶也一同消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季也是  小春也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊太也是  諾艾爾也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還傷害了汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳已經記起來我們的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽一定不會原諒我做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會認為我是她值得驕傲的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許從一開始  就沒有這樣認為過也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼乃乃香會在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  妳是過來見妳媽媽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且妳是下定了決心去面對她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我和湊太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香的話沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…絕對沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不容許任何反駁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從天文臺那時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香就是值得我驕傲的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能不能再等會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再給我一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先過去等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到這個季節了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像星星一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪下得好大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是汐音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  汐音你最後還是來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像從前那樣說說話如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  剛才汐音…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戶川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚大家在湖邊集合看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音見過乃乃香的媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我們成為朋友創造契機的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心想和她成為朋友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就笑得更燦爛些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不要這樣愁眉苦臉的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記憶中的乃乃香也一直都是笑容滿面的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳媽媽也一定想看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的乃乃香的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸先生在高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  它現在一定在感謝諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說「我好高興」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且小春也不用傷心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春不會去買新的怪獸先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小春說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這只霧龍對她來說是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是這麼喜歡這只霧龍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想要拜託柚季和湊太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季畫出形態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我切割木板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後和小春三人一起上色完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家一起做出來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香那時的笑容  不知給過我多少次勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說這一定是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香一直都很珍視媽媽說的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  挺起胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來見妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多快見到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  沒能去看妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年就拜託給乃乃香了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫古宮乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我成為朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是爸爸的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說今年因為工作原因不能來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  妳先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了答謝湊太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和湊太有好好努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然確實和原來有點不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸先生  恢復健康了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實呢  或許這樣也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}我都說可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}因為我可是看板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:21:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}流星雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}嗯  雖然還要再等幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}到時能看見很多流星從夜空中劃過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}小汐音也來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}好美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}流星雨還要更閃耀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}嗯  到那時我們一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}星星也在看著妳們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}像是在微笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.73,0:22:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}一定是因為妳們也在笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}汐音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.69,0:23:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}汐音讓我轉告妳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}曾想和妳一起去看流星雨的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}曾想和她一起去看流星雨的
